<doc id="1063589" wikidata="Q5705275" url="?curid=1063589" title="Batchi">
<text>Batchi (, also Romanized as Baţchī) is a village in Firuraq Rural District, in the Central District of Khoy County, West Azerbaijan province, Iran. At the 2006 census, its population was 56, in 15 families.

